  "remarks": "\nMariya Aleksandrovna ZAKHAROVA (‘M. ZAKHAROVA’) is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because (i) M. ZAKHAROVA is obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia and (ii) M. ZAKHAROVA is a member of, or associated with, a person who is or has been so involved. \n",
